PI_name.0: V. Angelopoulos, S. Mende & E. Donovan

TEXT.0: THEMIS Ground Based Observatory part of the THEMIS GBO effort. The All-Sky-Imagers (ASI) take white lght images of the overhead sky. N-S Keograms are generated by combining the North-Southcross section of the image from each UT time into a single image with UT time as x-axis.

Logical_source_description.0: Ground-based All Sky Imager (ASI), 3-sec N-S Keograms ordered by longitude, THEMIS GBO network

LINK_TITLE.0: Instrument description including data modes, products and caveats
